<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:37:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>iPad键盘贴纸展示</title><link>https://some.pics/6a03817d21b7d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;- iPad键盘保护套上的贴纸。按顺时针方向：
 - 完美星形支持者，代表我的朋友与邻居[香农+杰米·柯蒂斯](shannoncurtis.net)及其音乐。
 - [今天改进点什么](https://improvesomething.today)。有趣的小众网站，本月上线整整10年了。
 - 我们都漂浮在太空中。说得没错。
 - [莱克斯·罗曼的传奇](https://www.revenuerulebreaker.com)，如果你为自己工作并且在线开展业务，值得一看。
 - 可爱的小书柜图标❤️
 - 我在华盛顿州皮尔斯县投了票。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="- Stickers on iPad keyboard case. Clockwise from top:
  - Misfit Stars AKA supporter of my friends and neighbors [Shannon + Jamie Curtis](shannoncurtis.net) and their music.
  - [Improve Something Today](https://improvesomething.today). Odd little website, 10 years old this month.
   - We Are All Just Floating in Space. Correct.
   - [Lex Roman’s Legends](https://www.revenuerulebreaker.com), if you work for yourself and do any of it online you should take a look.
  -  Cute little library shelf ❤️
  - I Voted in Pierce County, Washington." height="3352" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chrkrhc/6a03817d21b7d.jpg" width="4470"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chrkrhc.some.pics"&gt;@chrkrhc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 19:37:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a034e9134a28</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被陷害&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A church tower stands against a grey sky behind a row of apartment blocks. The whole scene is framed by trees in the foreground. The picture is in black and white. " height="3864" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a034e9134a28.jpg" width="2898"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 16:00:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a033581520e9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一张有点骗人的照片。看起来像楼梯，但实际上是从下方拍摄的马德里的一座摩天大楼。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Una foto un poco mentirosa. Parecen escaleras pero es un rascacielos de Madrid desde abajo." height="3888" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a033581520e9.jpg" width="5184"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 14:13:27 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>晚安</title><link>https://some.pics/6a02ada4b85f1</link><description>&lt;p&gt;💤&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small black and white dog sleeps on a couch, on her side, with a man’s arm along her back and his hand on the back of her neck." height="2448" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jinx/6a02ada4b85f1.jpg" width="3264"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jinx.some.pics"&gt;@jinx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 04:33:43 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Machicomoco